Transform your Google Meet sessions into powerful, actionable insights with our Chrome Extension designed specifically for therapists. This tool simplifies client assessments by automatically transcribing your Google Meet conversations in real time, allowing you to focus more on your clients and less on note-taking.

Key Features:

Real-Time Transcription: Automatically transcribes your Google Meet sessions, providing a detailed record of client conversations for easier review and analysis.
Session Notes: Add notes or comments directly to the transcript during or after the session to highlight important points.
Secure Storage: Store transcriptions and client notes securely, ensuring client confidentiality and compliance with privacy regulations.
One-Click Save: Save your session transcripts and notes with a single click for easy future reference and assessments.
With our extension, therapists can streamline their workflow, improve the quality of their client assessments, and ensure that no important detail is missed during a session.

Simplify your client assessments today with automated transcription directly from Google Meet!
